The paper discusses reinforcement learning problems and the use of visual instructions composed of images or videos, which are common topics in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), robotics (cs.RO), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
